      <originalsloc id="aspace_9c97e4e03e47771e4eaaeb706e1b40c0">
         <head>Existence and Location of Originals</head>
         <p>The entire collection can be located on microfilm (HM 254) and in the Brazil and Portugal Collection (MS 1781).   This is a collection of correspondence and writings from and about Brazil related to Imperial Brazil, religious, economic, and geographic concerns. There is one item under the heading Portugal: a letter of condolence upon the death of a distant relative of Vasco de Gama.</p>  
      </originalsloc>
